@page "/"

<PageTitle>Frame Fisher</PageTitle>

<div class="d-flex align-center mb-4">
    <img src="img/fish1.jpg" alt="Frame Fisher Logo" style="max-width: 200px; height: auto; margin-right: 20px;" />
    <div>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Welcome to Frame Fisher</MudText>
        <MudText Class="mb-2">AI-Powered Video Search Across Your Entire Library</MudText>
    </div>
</div>

<MudAlert Severity="Severity.Info" ContentAlignment="HorizontalAlignment.Start">
    Frame Fisher uses <b>Reka Vision AI</b> to help you search, manage, and explore your video library with natural language queries.
</MudAlert>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">What is Frame Fisher?</MudText>
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
    Frame Fisher is an intelligent video search application that leverages advanced AI technology to make your video content searchable and discoverable.<br />
    Using Reka Vision's powerful visual understanding capabilities, you can search across multiple videos simultaneously using natural language.<br />
    <br />
    Simply describe what you're looking for, and Frame Fisher will find the relevant moments across your entire video library.
</MudText>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Key Features</MudText>
<br />

<MudText Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Smart Video Management</MudText>
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" GutterBottom="true">
    Add videos to your library and let Reka Vision AI process and understand their content.<br />
    Remove videos you no longer need with a simple interface.<br />
    Manage your entire video collection in one centralized location.
</MudText>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">AI-Powered Search</MudText>
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
    Search across all videos in your library using natural language queries.<br />
    Find specific scenes, objects, actions, or moments without manually reviewing hours of footage.<br />
    Get instant results powered by Reka Vision's advanced visual understanding.
</MudText>
